sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User/Flutter App
    participant A as Analytics Routes
    participant M as Auth Middleware
    participant C as Analytics Controller
    participant S as Analytics Service
    participant R as Redis Cache
    participant DB as MongoDB

    U->>A: GET /analytics/user/my/overview
    A->>M: Authenticate request
    M->>C: Forward if valid

    C->>S: getUserOverview(userId)
    
    S->>R: Get cache (analytics:user:{id}:overview)
    alt Cache Hit
        R-->>S: Return cached data
        S-->>C: Return analytics
    else Cache Miss
        S->>DB: Aggregate task data
        DB-->>S: Return aggregated data
        S->>S: Calculate streak
        S->>S: Calculate productivity score
        S->>R: Cache result (TTL: 5m)
        R-->>S: Cached
        S-->>C: Return analytics
    end

    C->>U: Send response with data
